Traveling to the End of the World
Mendicants I say its not possible to know or see or reach the end of the world by traveling
But I also say theres no making an end of suffering without reaching the end of the world
When he had spoken the Holy One got up from his seat and entered his dwelling
Soon after the Buddha left those mendicants considered
