This is the second thing
Having been born in a suitable family and married into a suitable family may I live at home without a cowife
This is the third thing
Having been born in a suitable family and married into a suitable family and living at home without a cowife may I have children
This is the fourth thing
Having been born in a suitable family and married into a suitable family and living at home without a cowife and having had children may I master my husband
This is the fifth thing
These are the five things that are hard to get for females who have not made merit
