Phoenixes
Both Kinds of Deeds
At Sāvatthī
Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha bowed sat down to one side and said to him
Sir what is the cause what is the reason why someone when their body breaks up after death is reborn in the company of the eggborn phoenixes
Mendicant its when someone does both kinds of deeds by body speech and mind
And theyve heard
The eggborn phoenixes are longlived beautiful and very happy
They think
If only when my body breaks up after death I would be reborn in the company of the eggborn phoenixes
When their body breaks up after death theyre reborn in the company of the eggborn phoenixes
This is the cause this is the reason why someone when their body breaks up after death is reborn in the company of the eggborn phoenixes
