There are the Gods of the ThirtyThree and those of Yama
also the Joyful Deities
the Gods Who Love to Create
and the Gods Who Control the Creations of Others
Set your heart on such places
and youll undergo delight
The Gods of the ThirtyThree and those of Yama
also the Joyful Deities
the Gods Who Love to Create
