Meditation
A Trainee
At Sāvatthī
Then a mendicant went up to the Buddha  and asked him
Sir they speak of this person called a trainee
How is a trainee defined
Mendicant its someone who has a trainees right view right thought right speech right action right livelihood right effort right mindfulness and right immersion
